(1, 'Privacy Policy', 'privacy-policy', '<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>\n<p>At HilDes, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal data is handled securely and transparently. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you interact with our website and services.</p>\n<h3>Information We Collect</h3>\n<p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Personal Information</strong><br>When you contact us or use our services, we may collect details such as your name, email address, phone number, and company information.</li>\n<li><strong>Technical Data</strong><br>We may collect IP address, browser type, device information, and usage behavior to improve user experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Communication Data</strong><br>Any information you provide through contact forms, emails, or support requests.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>\n<p>We use your data to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Provide and improve our services</li>\n<li>Respond to inquiries and communicate with you</li>\n<li>Personalize user experience</li>\n<li>Ensure security and prevent fraud</li>\n<li>Comply with legal obligations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We do not sell or rent your personal data to third parties.</p>\n<h3>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>\n<p>HilDes uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance website functionality and analyze user behavior. You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings.</p>\n<h3>Data Protection and Security</h3>\n<p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure. However, no online system is completely secure, and we encourage users to take precautions when sharing information online.</p>\n<h3>Third-Party Services</h3>\n<p>We may use trusted third-party tools and services (such as analytics or payment processors) that may collect and process data in accordance with their own privacy policies.</p>\n<h3>Your Rights</h3>\n<p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Access your personal data</li>\n<li>Request corrections or deletion</li>\n<li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>\n<li>Request data portability</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To exercise these rights, you can contact us at contact@hildes.io.</p>\n<h3>Data Retention</h3>\n<p>We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or comply with legal requirements.</p>\n<h3>Updates to This Policy</h3>\n<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\n<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact us:</p>\n<p>Email: contact@hildes.io<br>Website: https://www.hildes.io</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"Does HilDes sell my personal data?\",\"detail\":\"No, HilDes does not sell or rent your personal information to third parties.\"},{\"title\":\"What data does HilDes collect?\",\"detail\":\"We collect personal, technical, and communication data to provide and improve our services.\"},{\"title\":\"Can I request deletion of my data?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, you can request deletion of your personal data by contacting us.\"},{\"title\":\"How is my data protected?\",\"detail\":\"We use industry-standard security measures to safeguard your information.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you use cookies?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we use cookies to improve user experience and analyze website performance.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-28 08:39:34', 1, 1, '2026-04-28 08:39:34', '2026-04-28 08:39:34'),
(2, 'About HilDes', 'about', '<h2>About HilDes</h2>\n<p>HilDes is a modern software development company dedicated to building scalable, high-performance digital products. We specialize in AI-driven solutions, SaaS platforms, and custom web and mobile applications that help businesses innovate, automate, and grow.</p>\n<p>Our core focus is not just development — it is delivering solutions that solve real business problems and generate measurable results.</p>\n\n<h3>Our Expertise</h3>\n<p>At HilDes, we bring together technical excellence and strategic thinking to deliver impactful software solutions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>AI Development</strong><br>We build intelligent systems including RAG-based solutions, automation tools, and data-driven applications.</li>\n<li><strong>SaaS Development</strong><br>From MVP to enterprise-grade platforms, we create scalable SaaS products with multi-tenant architecture.</li>\n<li><strong>Custom Software Solutions</strong><br>Tailored systems designed around your business processes to improve efficiency and performance.</li>\n<li><strong>Web & Mobile Applications</strong><br>Fast, responsive, and user-centric applications using modern frameworks and technologies.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Our Approach to Building Software</h3>\n<p>We follow a streamlined and result-oriented process to ensure successful project delivery:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Discovery & Strategy</strong><br>We analyze your business model, target audience, and technical requirements.</li>\n<li><strong>System Design & Architecture</strong><br>We design scalable architectures that support long-term growth.</li>\n<li><strong>Agile Development</strong><br>We build iteratively with continuous feedback to ensure alignment.</li>\n<li><strong>Deployment & Optimization</strong><br>We launch efficiently and continuously optimize for performance and scalability.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3>Why Businesses Choose HilDes</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Outcome-driven development focused on ROI</li>\n<li>Scalable architecture built for long-term growth</li>\n<li>Clean and maintainable codebase</li>\n<li>Fast turnaround with agile workflows</li>\n<li>Reliable long-term technology partner</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Our Vision</h3>\n<p>Our vision is to empower businesses worldwide with innovative, scalable, and intelligent digital solutions that drive sustainable growth and competitive advantage.</p>\n\n<h3>Work With Us</h3>\n<p>Whether you are building an MVP, scaling your SaaS product, or integrating AI into your business, HilDes provides the expertise and execution needed to bring your ideas to life.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"What services does HilDes provide?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes provides AI development, SaaS platform development, custom software solutions, and web/mobile app development.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you work with startups?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we help startups build MVPs, validate ideas, and scale their products efficiently.\"},{\"title\":\"Can HilDes handle enterprise-level projects?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we design and develop scalable systems suitable for enterprise environments.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you offer post-launch support?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we provide maintenance, updates, and scaling support after deployment.\"},{\"title\":\"What technologies do you use?\",\"detail\":\"We work with modern technologies like React.js, Next.js, Node.js, Fastify, MongoDB, and AI frameworks.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-28 08:42:25', 1, 2, '2026-04-28 08:42:25', '2026-04-28 08:42:25'),
(3, 'Terms and Conditions', 'terms-and-conditions', '<h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>\n<p>Welcome to HilDes. These Terms and Conditions govern your use of our website and services. By accessing or using our platform, you agree to comply with and be bound by these terms.</p>\n\n<h3>Use of Services</h3>\n<p>By using our services, you agree to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>\n<li>Use our services only for lawful purposes</li>\n<li>Not engage in any activity that disrupts or interferes with our systems</li>\n</ul>\n<p>HilDes reserves the right to suspend or terminate access if these terms are violated.</p>\n\n<h3>Intellectual Property</h3>\n<p>All content, designs, code, and materials provided by HilDes are the intellectual property of HilDes unless otherwise stated.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You may not copy, reproduce, or distribute our content without permission</li>\n<li>Custom-developed solutions may be subject to separate contractual agreements regarding ownership</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Service Agreements</h3>\n<p>For project-based work, specific terms including scope, timelines, pricing, and deliverables will be defined in a separate agreement or contract. These agreements take precedence over general terms where applicable.</p>\n\n<h3>Payments and Refunds</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Payments must be made according to agreed milestones or invoices</li>\n<li>Delayed payments may result in project delays or suspension</li>\n<li>Refunds are subject to the terms defined in individual agreements</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Limitation of Liability</h3>\n<p>HilDes is not liable for:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>\n<li>Loss of data, revenue, or business opportunities</li>\n<li>Issues arising from third-party services or integrations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All services are provided \"as is\" without warranties unless explicitly stated.</p>\n\n<h3>Third-Party Services</h3>\n<p>Our solutions may integrate with third-party tools or services. HilDes is not responsible for the performance, policies, or reliability of these third-party services.</p>\n\n<h3>Confidentiality</h3>\n<p>We respect the confidentiality of client information and do not disclose sensitive data to unauthorized parties unless required by law.</p>\n\n<h3>Termination</h3>\n<p>We reserve the right to terminate or suspend access to our services at any time if terms are breached or misuse is detected.</p>\n\n<h3>Changes to Terms</h3>\n<p>HilDes may update these Terms and Conditions at any time. Continued use of the website or services constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>\n\n<h3>Governing Law</h3>\n<p>These Terms shall be governed and interpreted in accordance with applicable laws. Any disputes will be handled under the relevant legal jurisdiction.</p>\n\n<h3>Contact Information</h3>\n<p>For any questions regarding these Terms and Conditions, please contact us:</p>\n<p>Email: contact@hildes.io<br>Website: https://www.hildes.io</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"Do I need to agree to these terms to use HilDes services?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, by using our website or services, you agree to these Terms and Conditions.\"},{\"title\":\"Can these terms change over time?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, HilDes may update the terms, and continued use implies acceptance.\"},{\"title\":\"Are project-specific agreements separate?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, project contracts define detailed scope and override general terms when applicable.\"},{\"title\":\"Does HilDes offer refunds?\",\"detail\":\"Refunds depend on the specific agreement made for each project.\"},{\"title\":\"Is my data kept confidential?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, HilDes maintains strict confidentiality of client information.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-28 08:44:21', 1, 3, '2026-04-28 08:44:21', '2026-04-28 08:44:21'),
(4, 'Service Level Agreement (SLA)', 'sla', '<h2>Service Level Agreement (SLA)</h2>\n<p>This Service Level Agreement (SLA) outlines the service standards, support commitments, and performance benchmarks provided by HilDes for its AI solutions, SaaS platforms, and custom software services.</p>\n<p>Our goal is to ensure reliability, transparency, and consistent service quality for all clients.</p>\n\n<h3>Service Scope</h3>\n<p>This SLA applies to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>SaaS applications developed and maintained by HilDes</li>\n<li>AI-based systems and automation solutions</li>\n<li>Custom web and mobile applications under active support agreements</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Specific service terms may vary based on project contracts.</p>\n\n<h3>Service Availability (Uptime Guarantee)</h3>\n<p>HilDes is committed to maintaining high availability for all managed systems.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Target Uptime:</strong> 99.9% monthly uptime</li>\n<li><strong>Scheduled Maintenance:</strong> Pre-notified and typically conducted during off-peak hours</li>\n<li><strong>Unplanned Downtime:</strong> Actively monitored and resolved with priority</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Support Availability</h3>\n<p>We provide structured support to ensure smooth system operations:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Business Hours Support:</strong> Monday to Friday, standard business hours</li>\n<li><strong>Extended Support (Optional):</strong> Available based on agreement</li>\n<li><strong>Emergency Support:</strong> 24/7 support for critical issues (if included in contract)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Incident Response Time</h3>\n<p>We classify incidents based on severity levels:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Critical (Severity 1):</strong> System outage or major functionality failure — Response Time: Within 1 hour</li>\n<li><strong>High (Severity 2):</strong> Significant performance issues — Response Time: Within 4 hours</li>\n<li><strong>Medium (Severity 3):</strong> Partial functionality issues — Response Time: Within 8 hours</li>\n<li><strong>Low (Severity 4):</strong> Minor issues or general inquiries — Response Time: Within 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Resolution Time Objectives</h3>\n<p>While resolution times may vary depending on complexity, we aim to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Resolve critical issues as quickly as possible</li>\n<li>Provide continuous updates during issue handling</li>\n<li>Deliver permanent fixes after root cause analysis</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Maintenance and Updates</h3>\n<p>HilDes performs regular maintenance to ensure optimal performance:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Security updates and patches</li>\n<li>Performance optimization</li>\n<li>Feature enhancements (based on agreement)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Clients will be notified in advance of any planned maintenance.</p>\n\n<h3>Client Responsibilities</h3>\n<p>To ensure effective service delivery, clients are expected to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Provide accurate and timely information</li>\n<li>Report issues with sufficient detail</li>\n<li>Maintain secure access credentials</li>\n<li>Cooperate during troubleshooting processes</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Service Exclusions</h3>\n<p>This SLA does not cover:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Issues caused by third-party services or integrations</li>\n<li>Client-side misconfigurations</li>\n<li>Force majeure events (e.g., natural disasters, network outages beyond control)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>SLA Breach and Remedies</h3>\n<p>In case of failure to meet SLA commitments:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Issues will be escalated internally</li>\n<li>Service credits or remedies may be provided based on agreement</li>\n<li>Continuous improvements will be implemented</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Changes to SLA</h3>\n<p>HilDes may update this SLA periodically. Clients will be notified of significant changes affecting service commitments.</p>\n\n<h3>Contact and Support</h3>\n<p>For support requests or SLA-related queries:</p>\n<p>Email: contact@hildes.io<br>Website: https://www.hildes.io</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"What uptime does HilDes guarantee?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes provides a target uptime of 99.9% for supported systems.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you offer 24/7 support?\",\"detail\":\"24/7 support is available for critical issues if included in the service agreement.\"},{\"title\":\"How are incidents prioritized?\",\"detail\":\"Incidents are categorized into four severity levels based on impact and urgency.\"},{\"title\":\"What happens if SLA targets are not met?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes may provide service credits or remedies depending on the agreement.\"},{\"title\":\"Does SLA cover third-party issues?\",\"detail\":\"No, issues caused by third-party services are not covered under the SLA.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-28 08:46:59', 1, 4, '2026-04-28 08:46:59', '2026-04-28 08:46:59'),
(5, 'Why Choose HilDes', 'why-us', '<h2>Why Choose HilDes</h2>\n<p>Choosing the right technology partner can define the success of your product. At HilDes, we go beyond development — we focus on delivering scalable, reliable, and business-driven software solutions that create real impact.</p>\n\n<h3>Business-Focused Development</h3>\n<p>We do not just write code — we solve business problems. Every solution we build is aligned with your goals, whether it is increasing revenue, improving efficiency, or accelerating growth.</p>\n\n<h3>Expertise in AI, SaaS & Custom Software</h3>\n<p>HilDes specializes in high-demand, high-impact technologies:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>AI Development</strong> – Intelligent systems, automation, and data-driven applications</li>\n<li><strong>SaaS Platforms</strong> – Scalable, multi-tenant solutions designed for growth</li>\n<li><strong>Custom Software</strong> – Tailored applications built around your workflows</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This focused expertise ensures you get solutions that are modern, competitive, and future-ready.</p>\n\n<h3>Scalable Architecture from Day One</h3>\n<p>We design systems that grow with your business. Whether you are launching an MVP or scaling to thousands of users, our architecture ensures performance, reliability, and flexibility.</p>\n\n<h3>Fast and Agile Execution</h3>\n<p>Speed matters in today’s market. Our agile development approach allows us to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Deliver faster iterations</li>\n<li>Adapt to changing requirements</li>\n<li>Maintain high-quality standards</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You get a product that evolves quickly without compromising stability.</p>\n\n<h3>Clean, Maintainable Code</h3>\n<p>We follow best practices to ensure your codebase is:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Easy to scale and maintain</li>\n<li>Well-structured and documented</li>\n<li>Built for long-term sustainability</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This reduces technical debt and future development costs.</p>\n\n<h3>Transparent Communication</h3>\n<p>We believe in clear and consistent communication:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Regular updates and progress tracking</li>\n<li>Direct collaboration with developers</li>\n<li>Full visibility into project status</li>\n</ul>\n<p>No confusion, no hidden surprises.</p>\n\n<h3>Long-Term Partnership</h3>\n<p>We aim to be more than a service provider — we become your technology partner. From initial idea to scaling and optimization, we support your product at every stage.</p>\n\n<h3>Proven Development Process</h3>\n<p>Our structured approach ensures reliable delivery:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Discovery & Planning</li>\n<li>System Design</li>\n<li>Agile Development</li>\n<li>Deployment & Scaling</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This minimizes risks and ensures predictable outcomes.</p>\n\n<h3>Focus on Performance & Reliability</h3>\n<p>We build systems that are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fast and responsive</li>\n<li>Secure and stable</li>\n<li>Optimized for real-world usage</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Your users get a seamless experience, and your business gets consistent performance.</p>\n\n<h3>Work With Confidence</h3>\n<p>When you choose HilDes, you are choosing a partner committed to delivering quality, scalability, and measurable results.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"What makes HilDes different from other software companies?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes focuses on business outcomes, scalable architecture, and modern technologies like AI and SaaS.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you work with startups and enterprises?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we work with both startups and established enterprises.\"},{\"title\":\"How do you ensure project success?\",\"detail\":\"We follow a structured process, maintain clear communication, and build scalable solutions.\"},{\"title\":\"Can you scale my product as it grows?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, all systems are designed with scalability in mind.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you provide long-term support?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we offer ongoing support and maintenance after project delivery.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-28 08:48:37', 1, 5, '2026-04-28 08:48:37', '2026-04-28 08:48:37'),
(6, 'HilDes', 'home', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"What services does HilDes provide?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes provides AI development, SaaS platform development, MVP development, and custom software solutions.\"},{\"title\":\"Who are your ideal clients?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes works with startups, growing businesses, and enterprises.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you offer MVP development?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, HilDes helps startups build MVPs quickly.\"},{\"title\":\"Can you scale applications?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, HilDes builds scalable systems designed for growth.\"},{\"title\":\"How can I get started?\",\"detail\":\"You can contact HilDes through the website to discuss your project.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-28 08:50:26', 1, 6, '2026-04-28 08:50:26', '2026-04-28 08:50:26'),
(7, 'Software Development Services', 'services', '<h2>Software Development Services</h2>\n<p>HilDes offers a full range of modern software development services designed to help businesses build, scale, and innovate with confidence. From AI systems to SaaS platforms, we deliver solutions tailored to real business needs.</p>\n\n<h3>Our Core Services</h3>\n<p>We specialize in building high-performance digital products across multiple domains:</p>\n\n<h4>AI Development Services</h4>\n<p>We build intelligent systems that help businesses automate processes, analyze data, and improve decision-making.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>RAG-based AI systems</li>\n<li>Automation workflows</li>\n<li>AI-powered applications</li>\n<li>Data-driven solutions</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>SaaS Development Services</h4>\n<p>We design and develop scalable SaaS platforms built for long-term growth and multi-user environments.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Multi-tenant architecture</li>\n<li>Subscription & billing systems</li>\n<li>Admin dashboards</li>\n<li>Cloud-native solutions</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>MVP Development Services</h4>\n<p>We help startups turn ideas into market-ready products quickly and efficiently.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Rapid prototyping</li>\n<li>Lean MVP development</li>\n<li>Product validation</li>\n<li>Startup-ready architecture</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Custom Software Development</h4>\n<p>We build tailored software solutions designed around your business processes and goals.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Enterprise applications</li>\n<li>Workflow automation systems</li>\n<li>Internal tools</li>\n<li>Business-specific platforms</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Web Development Services</h4>\n<p>We create fast, responsive, and scalable web applications using modern frameworks.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Next.js / React applications</li>\n<li>High-performance websites</li>\n<li>API-driven architectures</li>\n<li>SEO-optimized builds</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Mobile App Development</h4>\n<p>We develop cross-platform and native mobile applications for seamless user experiences.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>iOS & Android apps</li>\n<li>Flutter / React Native solutions</li>\n<li>Scalable backend integration</li>\n<li>Performance optimization</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Our Approach</h3>\n<p>We follow a structured development process to ensure quality and scalability:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Requirement Analysis</li>\n<li>System Design & Architecture</li>\n<li>Agile Development</li>\n<li>Testing & Deployment</li>\n<li>Scaling & Support</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Why Choose HilDes Services</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Business-focused engineering approach</li>\n<li>Scalable and future-proof architecture</li>\n<li>Fast and agile delivery cycles</li>\n<li>Clean and maintainable codebase</li>\n<li>Long-term technical partnership</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Industries We Work With</h3>\n<p>We provide solutions across multiple industries including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>SaaS startups</li>\n<li>E-commerce businesses</li>\n<li>Enterprises</li>\n<li>Tech startups</li>\n<li>AI-driven platforms</li>\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"What services does HilDes offer?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes offers AI development, SaaS development, MVP development, custom software, web, and mobile app development.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you build SaaS products from scratch?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we design and develop full SaaS platforms including backend, frontend, and infrastructure.\"},{\"title\":\"Can you help startups build MVPs?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we specialize in building fast, scalable MVPs for startups.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you provide AI development services?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we build AI-powered systems including automation and RAG-based solutions.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you offer long-term support?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we provide maintenance, scaling, and post-launch support.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-28 08:52:01', 1, 7, '2026-04-28 08:52:01', '2026-04-28 08:52:01'),
(8, 'Case Studies', 'case-studies', '<h2>Case Studies</h2>\n<p>At HilDes, we do not just build software — we deliver real-world solutions that solve business problems and create measurable impact. Our case studies highlight how we help startups and enterprises turn ideas into scalable digital products.</p>\n\n<h3>What You Will Find Here</h3>\n<p>Our case studies showcase:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>AI-powered applications and automation systems</li>\n<li>Scalable SaaS platforms built for growth</li>\n<li>MVPs that helped startups validate ideas quickly</li>\n<li>Custom software tailored to business needs</li>\n<li>Web and mobile applications with real users</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Our Approach in Real Projects</h3>\n<p>Each case study reflects our structured development approach:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Understanding business challenges</li>\n<li>Designing scalable architecture</li>\n<li>Building with agile execution</li>\n<li>Deploying production-ready systems</li>\n<li>Optimizing for performance and growth</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Why Our Case Studies Matter</h3>\n<p>They demonstrate:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Real business impact, not just technical output</li>\n<li>Scalable architecture decisions</li>\n<li>Problem-solving approach</li>\n<li>Measurable improvements in performance or efficiency</li>\n<li>Long-term product success</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Industries We Have Worked With</h3>\n<p>Our work spans multiple industries, including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>SaaS startups</li>\n<li>E-commerce platforms</li>\n<li>Enterprise systems</li>\n<li>AI-driven products</li>\n<li>Service-based businesses</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Learn From Real Projects</h3>\n<p>Each case study helps you understand:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>How complex problems are solved using technology</li>\n<li>Why certain architectural decisions are made</li>\n<li>How scalable systems are built from scratch</li>\n<li>What results can be achieved with proper execution</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Build Your Next Project With Us</h3>\n<p>If you are inspired by our work, we can help you build your own product — from MVP to enterprise-scale systems.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"What type of projects are included in case studies?\",\"detail\":\"We include AI, SaaS, MVP, web, mobile, and custom software projects.\"},{\"title\":\"Do your case studies show real client work?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, they are based on real-world projects delivered by HilDes.\"},{\"title\":\"Can I request a similar solution for my business?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we can build custom solutions based on your requirements.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you share technical details in case studies?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we highlight architecture, approach, and outcomes where applicable.\"},{\"title\":\"Are case studies updated regularly?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we continuously add new projects as they are completed.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-28 08:54:53', 1, 8, '2026-04-28 08:54:53', '2026-04-28 08:54:53'),
(9, 'FAQs', 'faqs', '<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<p>This page answers the most common questions about our services, process, pricing, and technical capabilities. If you need more details, feel free to contact our team.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"What services does HilDes provide?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes provides AI development, SaaS platforms, MVP development, and custom software solutions.\"},{\"title\":\"How long does it take to build an MVP?\",\"detail\":\"Typically, MVP development takes between 4 to 8 weeks depending on complexity.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you provide ongoing support?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we offer post-launch support and SLA-based maintenance services.\"},{\"title\":\"What industries do you work with?\",\"detail\":\"We work across multiple industries including startups, SaaS businesses, and enterprises.\"},{\"title\":\"How do I get started?\",\"detail\":\"You can contact HilDes through the website to discuss your project and receive a proposal.\"}]', '[{\"category\":\"General Questions\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"What does HilDes do?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes is a software development company specializing in AI solutions, SaaS platforms, MVP development, and custom web and mobile applications.\"},{\"title\":\"Who do you work with?\",\"detail\":\"We work with startups, growing businesses, and enterprises looking to build or scale digital products.\"}]},{\"category\":\"Services & Expertise\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"Do you build AI-powered applications?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we develop AI systems including RAG-based solutions, automation tools, and intelligent workflows.\"},{\"title\":\"Can you build a SaaS product from scratch?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we design and develop scalable SaaS platforms, including multi-tenant architecture and subscription systems.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you offer MVP development?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we help startups quickly build MVPs to validate ideas and enter the market faster.\"}]},{\"category\":\"Process & Timeline\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"How long does a project take?\",\"detail\":\"Project timelines depend on complexity. MVPs typically take 4\\u20138 weeks, while larger systems may take several months.\"},{\"title\":\"What development process do you follow?\",\"detail\":\"We follow an agile methodology with iterative development, regular updates, and continuous feedback.\"}]},{\"category\":\"Pricing & Engagement\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"How much does a project cost?\",\"detail\":\"Costs vary depending on scope, features, and complexity. We provide custom quotes after understanding your requirements.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you offer fixed pricing or hourly models?\",\"detail\":\"We offer both fixed-price and flexible engagement models depending on the project.\"}]},{\"category\":\"Support & Maintenance\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"Do you provide post-launch support?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we offer maintenance, updates, and scaling support after deployment.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you provide SLA-based support?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we provide SLA-based support with defined uptime and response times.\"}]},{\"category\":\"Technical Questions\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"What technologies do you use?\",\"detail\":\"We use modern technologies such as React.js, Next.js, Node.js, Fastify, MongoDB, and AI frameworks.\"},{\"title\":\"Can you scale applications as traffic grows?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we design systems with scalability in mind to handle increasing users and data loads.\"}]},{\"category\":\"Security & Data\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"How do you ensure data security?\",\"detail\":\"We follow best practices including secure coding, encryption, and access control.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you sign NDAs?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we can sign NDAs to protect your business ideas and data.\"}]},{\"category\":\"Getting Started\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"How can I start a project with HilDes?\",\"detail\":\"You can contact us via our website or email to discuss your requirements and get a proposal.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you provide consultation?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we offer consultation to help you plan and define your project.\"}]}]', 1, '2026-04-28 09:02:39', 1, 9, '2026-04-28 09:02:39', '2026-04-28 09:02:39'),
(10, 'Contact Us', 'contact-us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"How can I contact HilDes?\",\"detail\":\"You can contact us through our website form or email us directly at contact@hildes.io.\"},{\"title\":\"How quickly will I get a response?\",\"detail\":\"We typically respond within 24 hours on business days.\"},{\"title\":\"Can I request a project quote?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, you can submit your project details to receive a custom quote.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you offer consultations?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we provide consultation to understand your requirements and suggest the best approach.\"},{\"title\":\"What information should I include in my inquiry?\",\"detail\":\"Include your project idea, goals, timeline, and any technical requirements if available.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-30 09:57:07', 1, 10, '2026-04-30 09:57:07', '2026-04-30 09:57:07'),
(11, 'Get a Quote', 'get-a-quote', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"How can I request a quote from HilDes?\",\"detail\":\"You can fill out the quote request form with your project details, and our team will get back to you.\"},{\"title\":\"What information should I provide for an accurate quote?\",\"detail\":\"Include your project scope, features, timeline, budget range, and any technical requirements.\"},{\"title\":\"How long does it take to receive a quote?\",\"detail\":\"We typically respond with an estimate within 24\\u201348 hours.\"},{\"title\":\"Is the quote free?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, requesting a quote is completely free.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you provide fixed-price estimates?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, we provide both fixed-price and flexible pricing models based on project needs.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-30 10:05:40', 1, 11, '2026-04-30 10:05:40', '2026-04-30 10:05:40'),
(12, 'Careers', 'careers', '<h2>Careers at HilDes</h2>\n<p>Join HilDes and be part of a team building scalable, high-impact digital products. We work on AI solutions, SaaS platforms, and custom software systems that solve real-world problems and drive business growth.</p>\n\n<h3>Why Work With Us</h3>\n<p>We offer an environment focused on growth, innovation, and meaningful work:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work on cutting-edge technologies (AI, SaaS, modern web stacks)</li>\n  <li>Opportunity to solve real business challenges</li>\n  <li>Collaborative and agile work culture</li>\n  <li>Focus on learning and continuous improvement</li>\n  <li>Flexible work environment</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>What We Look For</h3>\n<p>We are always looking for talented individuals who:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Have strong problem-solving skills</li>\n  <li>Write clean, scalable code</li>\n  <li>Understand modern development practices</li>\n  <li>Are proactive and growth-oriented</li>\n  <li>Can work in a collaborative environment</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Open Opportunities</h3>\n<p>We hire across multiple roles, including:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Full Stack Developers</li>\n  <li>Frontend Developers (React / Next.js)</li>\n  <li>Backend Developers (Node.js / APIs)</li>\n  <li>AI / Machine Learning Engineers</li>\n  <li>Mobile App Developers</li>\n  <li>DevOps Engineers</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Our Hiring Process</h3>\n<p>Our hiring process is designed to be efficient and transparent:</p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Application Review</li>\n  <li>Technical Assessment or Discussion</li>\n  <li>Interview (Technical + Culture Fit)</li>\n  <li>Final Decision</li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3>Growth &amp; Development</h3>\n<p>At HilDes, we invest in your growth:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Exposure to real-world scalable systems</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to work on diverse projects</li>\n  <li>Continuous learning and skill development</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Work With Impact</h3>\n<p>Every project you work on contributes to building products used by real businesses and users. Your work directly impacts product success and business growth.</p>\n\n<h3>Apply Now</h3>\n<p>If you’re passionate about building scalable software and working on modern technologies, we’d love to hear from you.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"What kind of roles does HilDes offer?\",\"detail\":\"HilDes offers roles in frontend, backend, full-stack development, AI engineering, mobile development, and DevOps.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you offer remote opportunities?\",\"detail\":\"Yes, depending on the role, remote or flexible work options may be available.\"},{\"title\":\"What technologies should I know?\",\"detail\":\"Familiarity with modern technologies like React.js, Node.js, and cloud-based systems is preferred.\"},{\"title\":\"How can I apply?\",\"detail\":\"You can apply through the careers page or contact us with your resume and portfolio.\"},{\"title\":\"What is the hiring process like?\",\"detail\":\"The process includes application review, technical evaluation, interviews, and final selection.\"}]', NULL, 1, '2026-04-30 10:08:32', 1, 12, '2026-04-30 10:08:32', '2026-04-30 10:08:32');

