(1, 'Insta Lab Test transformed how we manage appointments. It’s fast, intuitive, and has reduced our manual workload. Customers can now book tests effortlessly, improving both efficiency and overall satisfaction.', 'Michael Carter', 'Insta Lab Test', 'Operations Manager, Insta Lab Test', 'testimonials/GOHe9ZDYvftpCVxXDIXYsMo6fJlasD45gjmLiKJL.webp', 'michael-carter-insta-lab-test.webp', 'Michael Carter testimonial photo | HilDes', 1, 1, '2026-04-27 03:28:23', '2026-05-02 07:18:27'),
(2, 'British Fast Courier has streamlined our delivery operations from start to finish. The platform is fast, reliable, and makes managing shipments incredibly easy. Real-time tracking and smooth booking have improved our workflow and customer satisfaction significantly.', 'James Walker', 'British Fast Courier', 'Logistics Manager, British Fast Courier', 'testimonials/Kk6uTMYXKWBckS2olBAzxv0wl83Z8QQHgvEJsyKQ.webp', 'james-walker-british-fast-courier.webp', 'James Walker testimonial photo | HilDes', 2, 1, '2026-04-27 03:28:24', '2026-05-02 07:28:04');

